:Yet another fellow was caught in the name of Zeus. To appear in the second stage. His instrument is a basic set of [[Drum kit|drums]]. 
;Xenon Ishikawa 
:The fourth fellow that was caught in the name of Zeus. To appear in the third stage. His musical instrument is the simple [[bass guitar]]. 
;[[Zeus]] 
:In the final boss of the game, the enemy of the devil god demons appears to block progress towards beating it. He is named after the king of the [[List of Greek mythological figures|Greek gods]].

